    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Men or women who operate a drill, which is a large machine or hand tool used for making holes in a variety of materials. For workers that conduct the secondary process of enlarging or refining drilled holes to particular tolerances, use "borers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
